		<div>(Space Reserved for gear information section.)<br />
<br />
For reference, before any raid drops, a Bear can achieve, unbuffed:<br />
6000hp<br />
11500ac<br />
and enough str/agi to hold aggro substantially well.<br />
<br />
With raid drops, a Bear can break 10khp and hit the 15kac mark, with enough str/crit/agi to hold aggro over anyone. <br />
